{"tid":209369,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩叠碼仔被狂斬　浴血油麻地","createTime":"2017-04-20T07:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T11:57:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"174153ee674f5123a1a1695aec91cbbf430f0ded","tid":209369,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19995622&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19995622%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170420&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=0b9813fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19995622%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170420&h=86ffa880\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19995622&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170420</a><br />\n<br />\n兩叠碼仔被狂斬　浴血油麻地<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】油麻地昨清晨發生當街斬人案，兩名「叠碼仔」乘坐的士到文明里下車時，6至7名持刀惡煞駕車追至，撲出向2人追斬，2人手腳中多刀，負傷逃命，最後不支倒地，浴血街頭。刀手傷人後即登上接應車輛逃去，警方正追緝兇徒下落。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n救護員到場為傷者施救。 江寶龍攝<br />\n<br />\n疑有金錢瓜葛<br />\n<br />\n被斬傷2人分別姓李（39歲）及姓林（29歲），李情況嚴重而林情況危殆。消息指2人是叠碼仔，疑與金錢問題與人結怨惹禍，而兇徒均為本地漢。案件列作傷人案，交由油尖警區反黑組接手調查。兩名傷者遇襲後一度拒絕向警方透露遇襲經過及刀手人數等，警員要在附近店舖翻查閉路電視蒐證。<br />\n昨晨7時許，2事主在尖沙嘴截乘一輛的士前往油麻地，當的士到彌敦道與文明里交界下車時，突有兩部車馳至停車，6至7名手持利刀的大漢從車上撲出，向2人追斬。<br />\n2人一度返回車內躲避，但兇徒不肯罷休繼續用刀向他們襲擊，2人分別左手及雙手受傷，車廂遺下大灘血迹，2傷者負傷逃至彌敦道路口不支倒地。兇徒傷人後登上一輛私家車及一輛客貨車逃去，救護員到場替2傷者包紮後送院治理。<br />\n■記者江寶龍、黃江奇"},{"pid":"a5f77e1992138f8ea5c77729c9c424d5d5b2f78d","tid":209369,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T07:13:19.000Z","msg":"救護員到場為傷者施救。 江寶龍攝<br />\n<img src=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19995622&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170420\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19995622%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170420&h=79f7b1c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4501a0444fb4b57656092788968edd32ee9b9c55","tid":209369,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T07:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黑打黑"},{"pid":"5c217a212ad50dab1e8f9f03d50bac8646e92d5e","tid":209369,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:31:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b9b60c61fe6dc2790f280e18ab2e17572d80308","tid":209369,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"文明里"},{"pid":"d0312ffd7a820ef8278cf2a6c02751524b920b13","tid":209369,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T10:21:50.000Z","msg":"的士佬唔開車食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb0fe735a1ddae8cc030019c8fa04753e2ef6e6","tid":209369,"uid":14632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:42:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三國無雙咩屌😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真三國無雙<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">斬</span></span>"},{"pid":"21c758b6ccb159b7190cd99de6d30e2ba8a38b15","tid":209369,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>的士佬唔開車食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一陣開車搞到人斬唔到<br />\n比人mark埋就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783571b04e82b8fbb67897225429360a7a6ca16b","tid":209369,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:57:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>的士佬唔開車食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote